{"id":151994,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/facebook被指雇公关公司散布google负面消息/","date":"2011-05-13T00:30:41Z","modified":"2011-05-13T00:30:41Z","title":"Facebook被指雇公关公司散布Google负面消息","content":"<p>Daily Beast上的一篇报道声称，Facebook秘密雇佣了一家公关公司发布Google的负面消息。 文章称，有人雇佣了公关公司Burson-Marsteller，向新闻媒体散播Google负面新闻，指搜索巨人侵犯用户隐私。该公司邀请一位有影响力的博客写一篇抨击Google的评论，宣称可以发表在《华盛顿邮报》、Politico、The Hill, Roll Call、《赫芬顿邮报》等媒体上。这位博客却反而在Pastebin.com上公开了邮件内容。Daily Beast声称幕后公司是Facebook，表示社交巨人承认它雇佣了Burson-Marsteller。但Pcpro向Facebook的询问并未得到确认。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14c89e7d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=Facebook%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9B%87%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83Google%E8%B4%9F%E9%9D%A2%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F12%2F1122201%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=Facebook%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9B%87%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B3%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83Google%E8%B4%9F%E9%9D%A2%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F12%2F1122201%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092065010/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14c89e7d/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092065010/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14c89e7d/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=B5V0w4FNWpw:Rsv-P2V3vmo:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=B5V0w4FNWpw:Rsv-P2V